name: Sunwing Airlines Boeing 737 MAX 8 Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
Happy New Year! Sunwing Airlines is Canada's third Boeing 737 MAX operator, with a fleet of just two at the moment, C-FMXA and C-GMXB. Seen here is FMXA, taxiing by on Delta and departing runway 17L for Zihuatanejo, Mexico! ATC is included, hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
